page.title: 05BIRDS AND INSECTS
page.content: There are lots of birds in Auchnagatt, here are a few of them. {BLUETITS They are usually found in gardens looking for food.They are very common. {SPARROWS They live near houses and in gardens. Sparrows eat anything they can get there claws on! {THRUSH They eat snails,worms or anything they can find.They nest in trees and can be found anywhere with lots of trees. {CROWS Crows are very common around here.Thy are pests to farmers because they eat all corn and they eat anything and can be found anywhere mean .
